{"tid":1535294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美金已經俾我哋攞到要出全新鈔啦！","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:35:04.000Z","uid":292490,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"58422a42ba3e80260a1ad3aaed0e347468c2432a","tid":1535294,"uid":292490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"呢排去攞美金，銀行已經出動到全新連number未開封嘅鈔啦，大家繼續努力！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHnFShg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHnFShg.png&h=804ca5c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89de22031b67172cd0d7912b884e0b643b6790a2","tid":1535294,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:50.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cf70881b50491cf442f27ae252d8e448ea30e04f","tid":1535294,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d85bc4a512b8f594ee8f0633243e8fd11a49d27","tid":1535294,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"676b32b13c243f7e0934a0085ac5806fbdae6f17","tid":1535294,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"d儲蓄出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8668288e97298dd3fa30140e901685d01f83840","tid":1535294,"uid":256309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:07:45.000Z","msg":"最近拎個d又真係幾新淨"},{"pid":"3012aa4982b09d1f4cc2768421d3cab822b39a0e","tid":1535294,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"聽講中共有印美鈔"},{"pid":"fb924b737afa64c142ca61dae382e3ea50ad4588","tid":1535294,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58422a42ba3e80260a1ad3aaed0e347468c2432a","tid":1535294,"uid":292490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"呢排去攞美金，銀行已經出動到全新連number未開封嘅鈔啦，大家繼續努力！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHnFShg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http